# Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Character Voice-Over Performance

}}
This is a list of winners and nominees of the Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Character Voice-Over Performance.
In 2014, the award for Outstanding Voice-Over Performance was separated into two categories â€“ Outstanding Narrator and Outstanding Character Voice-Over Performance. As with longform and reality, this split acknowledges and accommodates a general industry uptrend in the distinctly different achievements that are VO narration and VO character performance.
